Description: GTK GUI for SSH TUN VPN routing
 SSH VPN GUI manages an OpenSSH TUN tunnel and local nftables routing rules
 from a GTK/Libadwaita desktop application. It includes a privileged helper
 for TUN, routing, firewall, and DNS classifier operations.
